text: Novaya Beryozovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 94 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Iglino, 3 km from Kaltymanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Novaya Beryozovka
